\">Park Collections</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">5</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Neighborhoods</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">6</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Park Type Guide</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">7</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Map &amp; Neighborhoods</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">8</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Planning Essentials</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">9</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Expert Advice</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">10</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Full Directory</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">11</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Owner &amp; Franchise</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">12</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">FAQs</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">13</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">More Resources</span></button></li></ul></nav><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-actions\"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn toc-action-top\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-up\"></i>Back to Top</button><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-down\"></i>To Bottom</button></div></div></div><main class=\"city-page-layout\"><div class=\"mobile-toc-button\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"mobile-toc-trigger\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-ul\"></i><span>Contents</span></button></div><section id=\"city-hero\" class=\"city-hero-section \"><div class=\"section-shell city-hero-shell\"><div class=\"city-hero-copy\"><div class=\"hero-breadcrumbs\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><span>Dog Parks Directory</span><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><strong>Salisbury</strong></div><p class=\"hero-eyebrow\">Historic Center</p><h1>Salisbury Strolls</h1><div class=\"hero-chip-row\"><div class=\"hero-chip\"><span class=\"chip-label\">Dog Park</span><span class=\"chip-value\">1</span></div><div class=\"hero-chip\"><span class=\"chip-label\">Greenway</span><span class=\"chip-value\">4+ mi</span></div></div><p class=\"hero-description\">Salisbury blends beautiful historic architecture with great green spaces. The Dog PAWS Park and the extensive Greenway system make it a hidden gem for dog owners.</p><div class=\"city-rich-description\"><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">Salisbury, North Carolina, offers a charming setting for dog owning, defined by its well-preserved historic downtown and its commitment to public parks. A walk through the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.visitsalisburync.com\">historic district</a> with a leashed dog is a journey through time, with wide sidewalks and beautiful architecture. For more vigorous exercise, the Salisbury Greenway offers over 4 miles of paved trails that weave through the city, connecting neighborhoods and offering a safe, traffic-free route for walkers and runners.</p><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">The city specifically caters to dog owners with <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/training-facilities\">excellent, fenced facilities</a> like the Dog PAWS Park at the Salisbury Civic Center. This fenced off-leash area is a community favorite, providing a dedicated space for socialization and play. Additionally, places like Dan Nicholas Park (just outside the city) offer a vast array of recreational options where leashed dogs can join the family for a day of fun. Salisbury combines the aesthetic appeal of a historic town with the functional amenities active dog owners need.</p></div><div class=\"hero-cta-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta primary\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-check\"></i>Browse directory</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta ghost\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i>Open map</button><a class=\"hero-cta text-link\" href=\"/list-your-park\"><i class=\"bi bi-plus-circle\"></i>Submit a park</a></div><div class=\"hero-footnotes\"><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Dog PAWS Park</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Salisbury Greenway</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->City Park</span></div></div><div class=\"city-hero-visual\"><div class=\"hero-image-card\"><img alt=\"Salisbury dog park landscape\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/salisbury-nc/hero.png\"/><div class=\"hero-image-gradient\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"city-premium-section\" aria-labelledby=\"city-premium-heading\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"city-premium-header\"><div><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Premium spotlight</span><h2 id=\"city-premium-heading\">Premium parks in <!-- -->Salisbury</h2><p>Partners highlighted here are currently investing in featured placement across this guide.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-header-actions\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">Feature my park</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to sales</a></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-values\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-megaphone\"></i></div><h4>Pinned above free listings</h4><p>Premium partners appear before every other card within the city directory.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-envelope-paper\"></i></div><h4>Lead-friendly CTAs</h4><p>Direct website + phone buttons encourage bookings straight from this page.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h4>Always-on exposure</h4><p>Featured cards show even when we haven’t processed new static data yet.</p></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-grid\"><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"city-insights\" class=\"city-insights-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><section id=\"city-statistics\" class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db city-stats-unified\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-section-header\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-eyebrow\">City Statistics</span><h2 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">How <!-- -->Salisbury<!-- --> stacks up for dog families</h2><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-intro\">Salisbury invites you to slow down. The tree-lined streets of the historic district are perfect for walks, and the parks offer ample space to run.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stats-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card accent\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Off-Leash</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Dog PAWS Park</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Located at the Civic Center, this fenced park offers a safe place for dogs to burn off energy and socialize.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Connector</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Salisbury Greenway</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">A network of paved trails connecting parks and neighborhoods. Scenic, flat, and great for miles of walking.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Classic</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">City Park</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">A beautiful traditional park with a lake, walking paths, and plenty of shade for a summer day.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db data-grid-container\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db key-metrics-grid\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item primary\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-geo-alt-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">31</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Total Dog Parks</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">All types combined</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-star-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">4.5</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Average Rating</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">Based on <!-- -->2,879<!-- --> reviews</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-chat-heart-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">2,879</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Total Reviews</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">Community feedback</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-trophy-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">17</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Premium Parks</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">4.5+ star ratings</span></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db charts-grid\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chart-card\"><h4 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">Park Types Distribution</h4><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chart-content\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bar-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bar-header\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bar-label\">Indoor Dog Park</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bar-value\">31<!-- --> parks</span></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bar-track\"><div style=\"width:100%;background-color:#6366f1\" class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bar-fill\"></div></div><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bar-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chart-ca