ic Center. There is also a small dog run at the Precious 9 Memorial Dog Park.\",\"category\":\"facilities\",\"popular\":true},{\"question\":\"Are dogs allowed on the Salisbury Greenway?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, leashed dogs are welcome on the entire 4+ mile greenway system. It is a fantastic way to explore the city’s creeks and woods.\",\"category\":\"planning\",\"popular\":true},{\"question\":\"Is Dan Nicholas Park dog-friendly?\",\"answer\":\"Leashed dogs are allowed in the park grounds and on trails, but they are not permitted in the zoo, carousel, or other specific attractions.\",\"category\":\"facilities\"},{\"question\":\"What is the leash law in Salisbury?\",\"answer\":\"Salisbury and Rowan County generally mandate that dogs be under restraint, which typically means a leash, harness, or being within a secure fence.\",\"category\":\"legal\"}],\"supportCard\":{\"kicker\":\"Visitors\",\"title\":\"Historic Tour\",\"description\":\"Grab a coffee downtown and take a self-guided walking tour.\",\"primary\":{\"label\":\"Walking Map\",\"href\":\"/history\"},\"secondary\":{\"label\":\"Events\",\"href\":\"/events\"},\"footnote\":\"History unleashed.\"}}]}]}]\n3d:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"related-resources\",\"className\":\"related-resources-section\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-heading\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"section-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"Keep exploring\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"More ways to plan\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Browse statewide guides, submit a listing, or connect with our team.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"resources-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"className\":\"resource-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"resource-icon\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-globe\"}]}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"California overview